511
00:29:35,374 --> 00:29:37,374
Dia memakainya tiap hari.

512
00:29:38,513 --> 00:29:39,513
Jaksa.

513
00:29:39,513 --> 00:29:42,614
Apa korban mengenakan sepatu
militer saat kejadian itu terjadi?

514
00:29:42,684 --> 00:29:44,414
