524
00:30:13,874 --> 00:30:16,043
...bersikap seperti
pembela terdakwa.

525
00:30:18,783 --> 00:30:19,884
Dia melontarkan
opini subjektifnya...

526
00:30:19,884 --> 00:30:21,354
