625
00:36:32,723 --> 00:36:36,164
Lalu Anda meraih
gunting lalu menikamnya.

626
00:36:36,593 --> 00:36:39,394
Kenapa ada gunting
di lantai rumah Anda?

627
00:36:50,104 --> 00:36:51,513
Di jaketnya...

628
00:36:52,444 --> 00:36:53,644
Silakan lanjutkan.

629
00:36:54,843 --> 00:36:57,883
Saku jaket suami
saya lobang.

