lain selain membunuhnya.

636
00:37:43,194 --> 00:37:44,834
Gunakan logika Anda.

637
00:37:45,033 --> 00:37:46,834
Dia berselingkuh.

638
00:37:46,834 --> 00:37:50,434
Suami mana yang takkan
marah apalagi dia tengah mabuk?

639
00:37:50,763 --> 00:37:53,473
Dia mungkin memukulinya,

640
00:37:53,703 --> 00:37:55,473
